data.text:
HOMETOWN HEROES

Our City Edition Collection celebrates the bond between a team and the town they call home. Inspired by iconic city symbols and past Houston Rockets uniforms, this tee highlights the unique cultures, communities and history that set Houston apart.

Lightweight Comfort

Double-knit mesh is lightweight yet durable, and is designed to help keep you cool.

Stay Dry

Dri-FIT Technology wicks sweat away from your skin to help you stay dry and comfortable.
